name: Before the Fall of Talos
description: 2021, video, 1920x1920x15s loop... When at last he beheld this object of beauty, his heart sang with pride and joy. Then quickly guilt and doubt set in, for the perfect forms were not by his hands but by the machine he had been building for days. Distraught he ran to the edge of the cliff ready to toss it over, or himself, for he would never be able to create again. He stopped at the abyss and turned as he heard his beloved teacher’s footsteps…
